Class VehicleType

    public class VehicleType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<VehicleType>
    The class used to represent groups of vehicles, here known as VehicleTypes. This class contains a unique id for the type of vehicle, then a name to describe it and a decimal number containing the supposed price per day.
